================================================================================
License Boundary
================================================================================

The app/ and sync_app/ components are separate programs that communicate
exclusively via TCP localhost sockets (JSON-RPC 2.0). They are not linked
or combined into a single executable. This architectural separation ensures
that the Apache-2.0 licensed Flutter app remains independent of the
GPL-3.0 licensed sync service.
